			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4660376">
									

<p>I'd want it to be an anime. Because damn all the anime tropes and antics would be ball-bustingly hilarious alongside the cosmic horror. I would want it to be mixed-genre, having both the deep and terrifying complex plots and light-hearted funny stupid story arcs. Focusing too much on one character, tone, or genre would take away from the diversity and richness of the SCP universe, where there's everything from Dr Bright drawing hentai to conspiracy scandals to human/mosquito romance to an extradimensional threat that kills you if you think about it. Presenting all this complexity while still giving fair attention to each character and story would be very difficult, but not impossible.</p>

